{"tid":1941672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★夫婦誤解魚缸清潔劑能治新冠肺炎　飲用後夫亡妻危","createTime":"2020-03-24T14:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T21:31:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"da2ad49cfd760f2f89d1ce07551085ecf82288c7","tid":1941672,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:24:31.000Z","msg":"美國亞利桑那州一對年逾花甲的夫婦懷疑誤解總統特朗普之說，誤以為一款魚缸清潔劑有抑制新型冠狀病毒療效，服用之後夫死亡妻危重。<br />\n<br />\n該對60多歲的夫婦居馬里科帕縣（Maricopa County），有疑似染病徵狀，但沒有接受病毒測試。當局初步認為他們沒染疫。<br />\n<br />\n上周四（19日），特朗普曾在記者會透露當局正試驗氯奎因（chloroquine）用來醫治新冠肺炎的療效。女事主懷疑因此以為那跟清潔魚缸用的「磷酸氯奎」（chloroquine phosphate）相同，夫婦倆在周一（23日）拿了一點混入液體飲掉以求防疫。結果不出20分鐘，兩人同告不適。男事主呼吸困難，抵達醫院不久後不治，女事主則曾嘔吐大作，其後危殆。當地衛生中心周一公布此事，警告民眾切勿藥石亂投。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普周一重申，他相信抗瘧疾藥物硫酸氯喹（hydroxychloroquine；跟氯奎因同類）與抗生素阿奇霉素（azithromycin）的組合，可遏制新冠肺炎全球大流行。他說紐約最快周二起可着手臨牀治療實驗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200324/s00005/1585049339889/%e7%be%8e%e5%a4%ab%e5%a9%a6%e8%aa%a4%e8%a7%a3%e9%ad%9a%e7%bc%b8%e6%b8%85%e6%bd%94%e5%8a%91%e8%83%bd%e6%b2%bb%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e-%e9%a3%b2%e7%94%a8%e5%be%8c%e5%a4%ab%e4%ba%a1%e5%a6%bb%e5%8d%b1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200324%2Fs00005%2F1585049339889%2F%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%25a4%25ab%25e5%25a9%25a6%25e8%25aa%25a4%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e9%25ad%259a%25e7%25bc%25b8%25e6%25b8%2585%25e6%25bd%2594%25e5%258a%2591%25e8%2583%25bd%25e6%25b2%25bb%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-%25e9%25a3%25b2%25e7%2594%25a8%25e5%25be%258c%25e5%25a4%25ab%25e4%25ba%25a1%25e5%25a6%25bb%25e5%258d%25b1&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=72260d95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200324%2Fs00005%2F1585049339889%2F%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%25a4%25ab%25e5%25a9%25a6%25e8%25aa%25a4%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e9%25ad%259a%25e7%25bc%25b8%25e6%25b8%2585%25e6%25bd%2594%25e5%258a%2591%25e8%2583%25bd%25e6%25b2%25bb%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-%25e9%25a3%25b2%25e7%2594%25a8%25e5%25be%258c%25e5%25a4%25ab%25e4%25ba%25a1%25e5%25a6%25bb%25e5%258d%25b1&h=03d97f48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200324/s00005/1585049339889/%e7%be%8e%e5%a4%ab%e5%a9%a6%e8%aa%a4%e8%a7%a3%e9%ad%9a%e7%bc%b8%e6%b8%85%e6%bd%94%e5%8a%91%e8%83%bd%e6%b2%bb%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e-%e9%a3%b2%e7%94%a8%e5%be%8c%e5%a4%ab%e4%ba%a1%e5%a6%bb%e5%8d%b1</a>"},{"pid":"6fe6917ffed31a56343453cd6acee33a3d084533","tid":1941672,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:25:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be02bdb44e0e2d6a8158470dfae395a27ee5b03c","tid":1941672,"uid":207900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:26:10.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea602721401596cc54609939947a8346d9ca3ef2","tid":1941672,"uid":264245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:26:24.000Z","msg":"達爾文咁快手"},{"pid":"33f40d1a36d730cf469934886d8cf5237332975f","tid":1941672,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:26:41.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9e8054d3fe03c7d568a13fe2b65d440259d7c60e","tid":1941672,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea602721401596cc54609939947a8346d9ca3ef2","tid":1941672,"uid":264245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:26:24.000Z","msg":"達爾文咁快手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T14:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217be18b3f235b266e41c37b7b1c8c44c43b0765","tid":1941672,"uid":63154,"li